align with possible transactional or query processing delays hinted at in the hypothesis.\n- **IO Utilization**: Increased `io_util` for `tidb-tikv` supports the notion of storage layer bottlenecks.\n  \n### Conclusion\nThe hypothesis regarding the TiDB storage layer seems to hold weight given the traces and multiple component interactions showing anomalies:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"memory_usage\",\n    \"failed_query_ops\",\n    \"io_util\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"Decreased memory usage but increased failed query operations indicate processing problems.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"memory_usage (normal_median: 1440911360.0, fault_median: 784515072.0), failed_query_ops (normal_p99: 0.0, fault_p99: 501.27)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased IO utilization suggests storage bottleneck.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"io_util (normal_p99: 0.15, fault_p99: 0.32)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Spikes in error and server error ratio suggest application layer issues linked to TiDB interactions.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio (normal: 0.0, fault: 13.1), server_error_ratio (normal: 0.0, fault: 13.1)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased response times indicating interaction delays with TiDB.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max (normal_median: 15253.0, fault_median: 4262.5)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
